本集节目获得了电视评论员的普遍好评。《[[赫芬顿邮报|赫芬顿邮报]]》的迈克尔·帕斯夸（{{lang|en|Michael Pascua}}）称赞《宁静之机》“以人物带动（剧情）发展”的结构，但批评其中的俚语对白“听起来就像是[[音乐电视网|音乐电视网]]的戏剧作品”，让整集节目有“碰运气”之嫌<ref name="HP" />。帕斯夸对塔希尔饰演的人物予以好评，称：“我希望他能在以后的节目中重现，（哪怕）只是提醒大家，要有耐心，要心怀希望”<ref name="HP">{{cite web | archivedate = 2014-12-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141227104136/http://www.aoltv.com/2009/10/30/review-greys-anatomy-give-peace-a-chance/ | url = http://www.aoltv.com/2009/10/30/review-greys-anatomy-give-peace-a-chance/ | title = Review: Grey's Anatomy – Give Peace a Chance | publisher = AOL, Inc | work = The Huffington Post | date = 2009-10-30 | accessdate = 2014-12-27 | author = Pascua, Michael | deadurl = no }}</ref>。史蒂夫·玛什（{{lang|en|Steve Marsi}}）在《电视迷》（{{lang|en|''TV Fanatic''}}）中给予本集正面评价，称节目表现赢得了自己的尊重，此外，也称赞了塔希尔的角色<ref name="TF" />。玛什对谢柏德一角的发展感到满意，称他是“最好的（医生）”，他还认为威尔森的执导功力出色，有望获得[[艾美奖|艾美奖]]提名<ref name="TF">{{cite web | url = http://www.tvfanatic.com/2009/10/greys-anatomy-review-give-peace-a-chance/ | title = Grey's Anatomy Review: 'Give Peace a Chance' | publisher = SheKnows Entertainment | work = TV Fanatic | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100314095243/http://www.tvfanatic.com/2009/10/greys-anatomy-review-give-peace-a-chance/ | date = 2009-10-30 | accessdate = 2010-03-14 | author = Marsi, Steve | archivedate = 2010-03-14 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》的珍妮弗·阿姆斯特朗（{{lang|en|Jennifer Armstrong}}）对节目的看法有些矛盾，称“这种无时不在的全医疗式剧集也该结束了”<ref name="EW" />。不过，她觉得谢柏德在墙上绘出图形的情节“太妙了”，塔希尔的角色也很“可爱”<ref name="EW" />。在阿姆斯特朗看来，《宁静之机》已经有《[[急诊室的故事|急诊室的故事]]》的风格，而她不希望在《实习医生格蕾》中看到《急诊室的故事》的影子<ref name="EW">{{cite web |archivedate=2013-10-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131001021429/http://tvrecaps.ew.com/recap/greys-anatomy-recap-season6-episode7/https%3A//web.archive.org/web/20131001021429/http%3A//tvrecaps.ew.com/recap/greys-anatomy-recap-season6-episode7/ |deadurl=no |url=http://tvrecaps.ew.com/recap/greys-anatomy-recap-season6-episode7/ |title='Grey's Anatomy' recap: Surgical Precision |publisher=Time Inc |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2009-10-30 |accessdate=2014-12-27 |author=Armstrong, Jennifer }}</ref>。《[[電視指南_(雜誌)|电视指南]]》的亚当·布莱恩特（{{lang|en|Adam Bryant}}）觉得这集比《见我所见》更加出色，但对卡雷夫和亚当森发展出的浪漫情感不以为然。他在评论中总结指出，《宁静之机》“证明，梅莉迪丝·格蕾并不需要独自承当起节目中所有的重担”<ref name="TVG">{{cite web |archivedate=2011-08-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110828003658/http://www.tvguide.com/tvshows/greys-anatomy/episode-6-season-6/191535 |url=http://www.tvguide.com/tvshows/greys-anatomy/episode-6-season-6/191535 |title=Grey's Anatomy Episode Recap: 'Give Peace a Chance' Season 6, Episode 6 |work=TV Guide |date=2009-10-29 |accessdate=2014-12-27 |author=Bryant, Adam |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

卡丽·贝尔（{{lang|en|Carrie Bell}}）在《[[人物_(杂志)|人物]]》周刊发文，称赞这集节目在一众演员间取得了平衡。她钟爱艾萨克一角，觉得节目中的团队协作证明，“团队中容不下自我中心”<ref name="rogue">{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224095600/http://www.people.com/people/article/0%2C%2C20421775%2C00.html |deadurl=no |url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20421775,00.html |title=Grey’s: McDreamy Goes Rogue |publisher=Time Inc |work=People |date=2009-10-30 |accessdate=2014-12-27 |author=Bell, Carrie |archivedate=2013-12-24 }}</ref>。前《[[明星纪事报|明星纪事报]]》（{{lang|en|''Star-Ledger''}}）编辑[[阿兰·塞平沃尔|阿兰·塞平沃尔]]（{{lang|en|Alan Sepinwall}}）觉得节目有好的开场，还赞扬了剧中主题的转变和谢柏德一角的发展<ref name="AS">{{cite web | last = Sepinwall | first = Alan | date = 2009-10-30 | url = http://sepinwall.blogspot.com/2009/10/greys-anatomy-give-peace-chance-eeeny.html | title = Grey's Anatomy, 'Give Peace a Chance': Eeeny-meeny diaper genie | work = What's Alan Watching? | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131212211629/http://sepinwall.blogspot.com/2009/10/greys-anatomy-give-peace-chance-eeeny.html | publisher = Blogspot | accessdate = 2014-12-27 | archivedate = 2013-12-12 }}</ref>。格伦·迪亚兹（{{lang|en|Glenn Diaz}}）在{{lang|en|[[BuddyTV|BuddyTV]]}}网站发文，称这集节目有浓厚的喜剧色彩，例如罗宾斯挺身而出阻止韦伯的情节就“太搞笑了”，杨也是这集的“开心果”<ref name="BTV">{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131224113009/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/greys-anatomy/greys-anatomy-give-peace-a-cha-32279.aspx | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/greys-anatomy/greys-anatomy-give-peace-a-cha-32279.aspx | title = 'Grey's Anatomy' 'Give Peace a Chance' Recap – The Mother of All Tumors and Diapers | publisher = BuddyTV | date = 2009-10-29 | accessdate = 2014-12-27 | author = Diaz, Glenn | archivedate = 2013-12-24 | deadurl = yes | df =  }}</ref>。在{{lang|en|AfterEllen.com}}网站的一位资深编辑看来，谢柏德和韦伯之间持续不断的争执有些没完没了到令人厌烦<ref name="ILCUK">{{cite web | url = http://www.afterellen.com/blog/badmachine/greys-anatomy-mini-cap-give-peace-a-chance | title = 'Grey's Anatomy: mini-cap: 'Give Peace a Chance' | work = AfterEllen | publisher = Logo | date = 2009-11-02 | archivedate = 2012-11-27 | accessdate = 2010-02-09 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121127160428/http://www.afterellen.com/blog/badmachine/greys-anatomy-mini-cap-give-peace-a-chance }}</ref>。

《宁静之机》为彼得·诺沃克赢得了[[人道奖|人道奖]]60分钟节目类编剧提名<ref>{{cite web | title = Finalists Announced for 36th Annual HUMANITAS Prize Honoring Great Television and Film Writing | publisher = PR Newswire | accessdate = 2014-12-27 | date = 2010-07-14 | archivedate = 2013-12-24 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131224085311/http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/finalists-announced-for-36th-annual-humanitas-prize-honoring-great-television-and-film-writing-98438949.html | url = http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/finalists-announced-for-36th-annual-humanitas-prize-honoring-great-television-and-film-writing-98438949.html }}</ref>。威尔森也因执导本集获[[有色人种促进协会形象奖|有色人种促进协会形象奖]]正剧剧集类杰出导演奖<ref name="Award">{{cite web | title = 2010 NAACP Image Awards winners: Darryl 'Chill' Mitchell, Precious, Chris Rock and more | publisher = Tribune Company | work = Zap2it | date = 2010-02-26 | accessdate = 2014-12-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140912043743/http://www.zap2it.com/blogs/2010_naacp_image_awards_winners_darryl_chill_mitchell_precious_chris_rock_and_more-2010-02 | archivedate = 2014-09-12 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.zap2it.com/blogs/2010_naacp_image_awards_winners_darryl_chill_mitchell_precious_chris_rock_and_more-2010-02 }}</ref>。

